snippet.title: Willy's Wonderland: The Game - Mobile Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Willy's Wonderland is now available for Mobile devices!
More info:
https://bit.ly/WillysAndroid

Willy’s Wonderland – The Game is a 2.5D beat ‘em up game based on the cult film of the same name, in which a group of Animatronics come to life and slaughter people who dare visit Willy’s Wonderland.

Players take control of either The Janitor or Liv as they face the hordes of evil commanded by the nefarious Animatronics - Tito Turtle, Siren Sara, Arty Alligator, Cammy Chameleon, Willy Weasel and more!

Try different combinations of punches and kicks to perform different combos and make use of special techniques and powerful abilities to get rid of Willy and his henchmen.
_______________________________

About QUByte Interactive
QUByte is the largest Latin American developer and publisher of console games. Our goal is to develop the industry through Porting and Publishing partnerships leading games, which we once rated their limited reach, to all available platforms.


About Mito Games
MITO GAMES is a company from Espirito Santo (Brazil) that offers for the players a different way to learn, have fun and for our business customers an innovative way to communicate with your target. They believe that all histories and knowledge could be delivered through them, as even the MYTHS. 



All rights reserved © 2021 QUByte Interactive.
